---

Before implementing backend code:

1. Read AGENTS.md.
2. Read docs/architecture.md.
3. Read docs/backend-conventions.md.
4. Read docs/coding-style.md.

Then inspect an existing backend module similar to the requested feature.

Follow existing architecture.

Do not introduce new folder structures.

Do not introduce new frameworks.

Follow dependency injection patterns already used in the project.

Run build if possible before finishing.